transArray.content: The room was very clean and the internet connection was super convenient. It had been cleaned when I came back. It was very comfortable and the room was very cozy. The little robot that delivers food is also very cute hahaha.

Dear family, if I can't be a big tree to protect you from wind and rain, I can be a flower to decorate your journey; if I can't be a sailor to control the boat, I can be an oar to protect you. Love you little man
